{"tid":2054163,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[紅雨行山/鬼佬做就係型] 外籍行山客冒雨登大帽山　被困山頂雷達站","createTime":"2020-06-07T02:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T16:10:15.000Z","uid":132782,"like":27,"dislike":197,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"afbc54edffaccc5b1984cf9f60680c697d78e8da","tid":2054163,"uid":132782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>06月07日(日) 08:12</strong><br />\n<br />\n暴雨下有行山客被困大帽山。<br />\n<br />\n5名外籍行山客，昨夜(6日)參加行山活動冒雨登上大帽山，豈料至今晨(7日)7時許雨勢轉大，一行人在山頂雷達站被洪水圍困未能落山，於是報警。消防接報後出動展開營救，成功尋獲5人。<br />\n<br />\n眾人於救護車檢驗無大礙後自行離開，有行山人士親友得悉事件亦到達現場了解。<br />\n<br />\n五人獲救經檢驗無大礙後自行離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200607/photo/bkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=135b21ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被困行山客與親友會合，眾人鬆一口氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200607/photo/bkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_02b.jpg&h=2ad61d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防、救護及警方到場救援。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200607/photo/bkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200607081215820-0607_00822_001_04b.jpg&h=59cc64e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncredit: 東方日報 <br />\n<br />\n型:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柒:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ec492c913fee2f5fe5b293aabc027b2c5a1ec9","tid":2054163,"uid":132782,"like":30,"dislike":7,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/